			Aquatic Resource Spawn

| Resource Name        | Type / Description                                                      | Mechanics / Location                                                                           |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Glassfin Coral   | Bioluminescent coral that can be harvested for crafting potions or dyes | Hidden side caverns, only accessible during low tide                                       |
| Moonlit Pearl    | Rare pearl found in oysters embedded in rock walls or mini-reefs        | Spawns in water pools with reflected light; chance increases with smuggling route activity |
| Silverwater Kelp | Kelp that enhances temporary underwater stamina                         | Found along walls of pocket caverns; can be harvested for consumables                          |

* Optional Trigger : Smuggling quests completed boost spawn rate of Glassfin Coral and Moonlit Pearl

